<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg001.perseus-grc1:409\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Supp.\">Supp.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">409</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὕδατος, μελίσσης, μηδὲ προσφέρειν μέθυ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg007.perseus-grc1:481\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ OC\">OC</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">481</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:77\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.77</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n67299.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> in <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μηδέ . . μηδέ</foreign>. . the first <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μ.</foreign> may belong to <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μηδέ</foreign> A, e.g. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:303\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.303</biblScope> </bibl> sq., or to <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μηδέ</foreign> B, e.g. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg030.perseus-grc1:391c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ R.\">R.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">391c</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">μήτε . . μηδέ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0033.tlg004.perseus-grc1:2:45\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pi.\">Pi.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ I.\">I.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.45</biblScope></bibl></cit>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg022:327d\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Prt.\">Prt.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">327d</biblScope> </bibl>; but <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μήτε</foreign> cannot follow <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μηδέ</foreign>:—for <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μηδέ</foreign> after <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὐδέ</foreign>, <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">v.</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">οὐ</ref> </xr> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.3</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"B\" id=\"n67299.2\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> as <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adv.\">Adv.</a></pos>, joined with a single word or phrase, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">not even, not either</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:21:375\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.375</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:4:710\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.710</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; repeated emphatically, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μηδ᾽ ὅντινα γαστέρι μήτηρ κοῦρον ἐόντα φέροι μηδ᾽ ὃς φύγοι</foreign> let <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">not</tr_> the babe unborn —<tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">no let not even</tr_> it escape, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:6:58\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.58</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὸ μήποτ᾽ αὖθις μηδ᾽ ἀναστῆναι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg005.perseus-grc1:569\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ag.\">Ag.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">569</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>:—for <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μηδέ τι</foreign> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">v.</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">μήτις</ref></xr>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}